thread.title: BRIEF-Choice Properties Qtrly FFO Per Unit $0.282

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Choice Properties Qtrly FFO Per Unit $0.282
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Choice Properties Real Estate Investment Trust:
* REPORTS CONTINUED GROWTH FOR THE FOURTH QUARTER OF 2017 * QTRLY NET INCOME PER UNIT DILUTED $0.088 * QTRLY FFO PER UNIT DILUTED $0.282 * QTRLY RENTAL REVENUE TOTALED $211.0 MILLION, UP 6.7% COMPARED WITH $197.7 MILLION LAST YEAR
* EXPECTS TO INVEST APPROXIMATELY $198 MILLION TO COMPLETE DEVELOPMENTS COMING ONLINE IN 2018
* Q4 FFO PER SHARE VIEW C$0.26 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
